# Workspace

> Member registry for a monorepo harness — the **single source of truth** for what counts
> as a member. Membership is never auto-guessed: only repos listed here are governed by the
> root harness. `Area` is a short, unique label you choose (not the stack name — two members
> can share a stack). `Stack` is the profile harness-kit detected for that path.
> Add a row to bring a new repo under the harness; remove one to drop it.

